{"id":615115,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【立此存照】以为是针对香港-结果是针对国内/","date":"2019-08-07T12:46:53Z","modified":"2019-08-07T12:46:53Z","title":"【立此存照】以为是针对香港 结果是针对国内","content":"<p>据微博@深圳公安 8月5日消息，为坚决打好打赢新中国成立70周年大庆安保攻坚仗，进一步凝聚警心、鼓舞士气、练兵备战，全力维护国家政治安全和社会平安稳定，根据省厅统一部署，深圳公安于8月6日10：30在宝安区海滨广场举行“广东公安夏季大练兵‘深圳亮剑’行动”。</p>\n<p>另据微博@南方都市报 报道，此次练兵于宝安区海滨广场进行，有1.2万名警力结集，内容涵盖特警科目演练、突发事件应急处置等，海陆空大片同步上演。</p>\n<p>来源：观察者网</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"（官方视频）深圳亮剑：超燃海陆空演练大片\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PA3fOMpuoPY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>然而，据网友报道分析视频分析后发现，该“深圳亮剑”行动显然是一次针对“农民工讨薪”的维权镇压行动，视频中出现有“还我血汗钱”、“违法欠农民工工资，良心何在”等标语。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBWPrKPUwAEC3X-.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615118\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBWPrKPUwAEC3X-.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"655\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBWPrKPUwAEC3X-.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBWPrKPUwAEC3X--206x300.jpg 206w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBWPrKPUwAEC3X--768x1117.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBWPrKPUwAEC3X--704x1024.jpg 704w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBSl0VkW4AUt7EU.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615119\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBSl0VkW4AUt7EU.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"878\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBSl0VkW4AUt7EU.jpg 1050w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBSl0VkW4AUt7EU-154x300.jpg 154w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBSl0VkW4AUt7EU-768x1498.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EBSl0VkW4AUt7EU-525x1024.jpg 525w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">十年间足以扭转很多常识 <a href=\"https://t.co/C6WcJ4JGup\">pic.twitter.com/C6WcJ4JGup</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; ドイツ總司令 ʕ移動準備完了! (@WasyiaKing777) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WasyiaKing777/status/1158990465452036097?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 7, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1012,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[21356,38564,38551,9503,13804,20761,38526]}